{"tid":2229717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸咁多位。成日話要放棄呀。又批鬥啊。麻煩入入嚟","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:57:52.000Z","uid":90520,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4341d44d80d217555b970b4f0f71f4d8f1f46fac","tid":2229717,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cq0K2ipTaPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCq0K2ipTaPM&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=5dac2d91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cq0K2ipTaPM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVZViHX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVZViHX.jpg&h=cee9b543&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6ggNBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6ggNBi.jpg&h=33dec952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奉勸咁多位。成日話要放棄呀。<br />\n又批鬥啊。麻煩入入嚟<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地睇左反校未？<br />\n<br />\n《返校》時間為1962年，軍事法庭捉拿政治犯風潮熾熱，但凡閱讀及討論赤共思想的書一律有罪、參與任何形式的地下活動公民抗命一律被逮捕成階下囚。而就讀翠華中學的一班師生便因舉辦地下讀書會捲入漩渦，本來期望以知識抵抗高壓統治，最後卻因「舉報機制」而弄至篤灰疑雲、人人心裡有鬼。《返校》取材自真人真事，當年基隆中學校長出版批評國民黨的《光明報》，最後導致多名師生被處決、撰稿者流亡海外，學校全面被查封。走筆至此彷如時空交錯身歷其境<br />\n<br />\n我知道最近好多人成日話呢話路<br />\n<br />\n電影中的一句：<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">「總得有人活下去，記得這一切有多得來不易。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n未來我們香港人可以說出這一句嗎？<br />\n<br />\n台灣可以在數十年後說一句「得來不易」，未來的香港可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n台灣。南韓。爭取民主。唔係一日半日的事<br />\n希望大家繼續努力吧<br />\n<br />\n其實香港人實在不太需要透過電影來警世，大家只要拿出勇氣走上街，電影的情節就實實在在發生於眼前&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJYi0YU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJYi0YU.jpg&h=8103ea05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5445374f4c6826f1b1500020618e5b83f6485933","tid":2229717,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"推幾下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392ac94d58caca6c112b9d35ea9efbbb11d877e8","tid":2229717,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uCvR7f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uCvR7f.gif&h=b3670f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npush<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef731a5697bd0be4aa93350d0d0ac2b613aeb73e","tid":2229717,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"有咁多人睇過咩？"},{"pid":"083c9b12cc9ef59d4a696e1e34b577a9010a0e42","tid":2229717,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef731a5697bd0be4aa93350d0d0ac2b613aeb73e","tid":2229717,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"有咁多人睇過咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"應該好多都無掛。無咪揾辦法睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ad3e764eb1089375eb25229fc2aeeb2209e742","tid":2229717,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2wTPVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2wTPVq.jpg&h=19c46307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作人林仕肯指今次把《返校》拍成劇集，透過 Netflix 這個平台讓全球的觀眾都有機會了解到台灣獨特的歷史，不只讓國際認識台灣，更讓他們接觸到台灣的故事，相信台灣的人民都會感到非常興奮。《返校》劇集將會於 12 月 5 日起上線，每逢星期六就會更新最新集數，全季共有 8 集。不論有沒有看過電影的觀眾，都絕對可以一看！"}]}